      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Attention Required: Timeliness of Daily Commute\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter that has come to my attention regarding your daily arrival times. It has been observed that you have arrived approximately 15 minutes late each day over the past two weeks. While we understand that occasional delays can occur, consistent tardiness is impacting the team's overall productivity and meeting our punctuality standards.\n\nAs a team, we value punctuality and reliability, and your timely arrival is a crucial part of our collective success. We kindly request that you adjust your departure time to ensure you arrive at work by the scheduled start time.\n\nWe appreciate your cooperation and understanding in this matter. Please feel free to reach out if there are any underlying issues that may be contributing to your tardiness.\n\nThank you for your prompt attention to this matter.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
      "source": "target",
