      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Urgent: Addressing Persistent Tardiness\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI trust this message finds you well. I am writing to formally address an issue that has been consistently observed over the past two weeks. Your arrival at work has been recorded as approximately 15 minutes late each day. This habitual tardiness is not only a breach of our punctuality policy but also a matter of concern that warrants immediate attention.\n\nOur warehouse operations rely heavily on the seamless coordination of our staff. Your late arrivals have inadvertently disrupted the workflow, causing delays that ripple through the entire team. The rest of the warehouse staff has expressed frustration, as they must adjust their schedules and tasks to accommodate your tardiness, often resulting in compromised productivity and increased stress levels.\n\nWe have given you the opportunity to rectify this situation, and we expect you to adhere to the scheduled start time henceforth. Should this pattern of tardiness persist, we will be compelled to consider disciplinary action as per our company policy.\n\nWe understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays. However, we urge you to take proactive measures to ensure punctuality moving forward. Your cooperation is essential in maintaining the harmony and efficiency of our warehouse operations.\n\nThank you for your immediate attention to this critical matter.",
